Content:
These are the crashing statements:<p><pre><code>  SELECT n()AND+#0;
  SELECT strftime()
  DETACH(SELECT group_concat(q));
  DROP TABLE IF EXISTS t0; CREATE TABLE t0(t);
  INSERT INTO t0 SELECT strftime();
  SELECT quote(t) FROM t0
</code></pre>
See <a href="https://www.sqlite.org/src/info/fe578863313128" rel="nofollow">https://www.sqlite.org/src/info/fe578863313128</a> for the patch.
